=== TEST 1: kong.log.inspect() pretty-prints a table
--- http_config eval: $t::Util::HttpConfig
--- config
    location /t {
        content_by_lua_block {
            local PDK = require "kong.pdk"
            local pdk = PDK.new()

            pdk.log.inspect({ hello = "world" })
        }
    }
--- request
GET /t
--- no_response_body
--- error_log
